sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant WS as WS /api/v1/events/subscribe

    Client->>WS: open WebSocket
    Client->>WS: subscribe with since + filters

    rect rgb(240, 232, 255)
        Note over Client,WS: replay from retention
        WS-->>Client: event seq=104701
        WS-->>Client: event seq=104702
        WS-->>Client: event seq=104836
    end

    rect rgb(232, 255, 232)
        Note over Client,WS: live
        WS-->>Client: event seq=104837
        WS-->>Client: event seq=104838
    end

    Note over Client,WS: since absent starts now
    Note over Client,WS: since evicted returns SinceOutOfRetention 4010
